** New Historical and Cultural Criticism
   West authored and west authorized. They believe history progressive. New historicism goes against that crap. It is centrally concerned, writings are produces within specific conditions that determined by such conditions. Historicity, specific cultural, social, tempera state in which it was composed. Texts are shaped by those conditions ans shape those conditions, mutually constitutive. 
